## MiniRover Student Purchase Program

### Not a requirement!

* Having your own MiniRover not required but it does add an extra level of fun to the course!
* You will be able to learn a lot and get a great grade without having your own robot
* Still getting your hands dirty with a physical robot adds a lot to the experience

### Purchase and Assembly

* We have arranged some discounts on some of these
* With discounts the total is $290
* We have arranged to have the robots assembled and tested for free
* For pickup in Waltham after payment
* If you want you can also do it all yourself

