### Parts

* This is for your information only. We will order the parts and assemble and test the robot for you. Assembly requires tools and a drill. It's not hard but then again, it's not for everybody.

* [GoPiGo3 - Base Kit](https://www.dexterindustries.com/store/gopigo3-base-kit/) - Pito will give you the contact
